       <table border="0" width="100%">             
 <tr>             
  <td width="100%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      
             
  <p class="a2" style="mso-outline-level:1" align="center">“来说”和“说来”<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:14.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;text-indent:21.0pt;
mso-outline-level:1"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-font-kerning:
1.0pt">程乐乐</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="right" style="text-align:right"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;;mso-font-kerning:
1.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt">“</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">来说”和“说来”这两个词语有时候可以替换，意思差不多，例如：“总的来说</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">/</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">说来、这样</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">(</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">么</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">)</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">来说</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">/</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">说来、大</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">(</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">小</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">)</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">的方面来说</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">/</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">说来、就此来说</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">/</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">说来”，这时“来说”和“说来”都表示是一种总结或推论，而且，有的去掉“来”，意思也不会改变，例如：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">1.总的来说/总的说来――&gt;总的说<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">2.这样(么)来说/这样(么)说来――&gt;这样(么)说</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">但是，在其他情况下，“来说”和“说来”是不能互相替换的。“来说”还表示“要发表意见”，例如：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt">3.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:楷体_GB2312">我来说两句。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">4.我来说说。<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">5.让约翰来说一下。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><br>
</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“说来”还表示对人对事物某一方面的情况进行估计。例如：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt">6.(a)</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:楷体_GB2312">这件事说来有两年多了。<span lang="EN-US"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">7.(a)说来你也不小了。<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">8.(a)说来话长。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><br>
</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">上面</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">3-8</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">中的“说来”和“来说”不能互换。在形式上还有这样的特点：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt">A.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“说来”中的“来”可以用“起来”替换，意思不会改变。例如：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:33.05pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;text-indent:-11.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">6.(a)这件事说来有两年多了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">――&gt;</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">(b)这件事说起来有两年多了。<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">7.(a)说来你也不小了。――&gt;(b)说起来你也不小了。<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">8.(a)说来话长。――&gt;(b)说起来话长。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><br>
</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">而“来说”中的“来”换成“起来”，就是“起来说”，是“站起来说”的意思，语义有了改变。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt">B.</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“说来”在句中作插入语，位置比较灵活，可以在主语的前面，也可以在主语和谓语之间，语义没有改变。例如：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt">6.(a)</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:楷体_GB2312">这件事说来有两年多了。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312">――&gt;</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:楷体_GB2312"><span lang="EN-US">(c)说来这件事有<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span>两年多了。<br>
<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>7.(a)说来你也不小了。――&gt;(c)你说来也不小了。<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“说来话长。”中的“话长”是主谓短语作谓语，这个句子没有主语。而“来说”一般在句子中作谓语，不能放在句子主语的前面</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">(</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">或者能放在主语前面，但意思变了</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">)</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.2pt"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">“来说”和“说来”的关系可以简要地总结成下表：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:22.2pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:9.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="margin-left:5.4pt;
 border-collapse:collapse;mso-table-layout-alt:fixed;border:none;mso-border-alt:
 solid windowtext .5pt;mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt">
  <tr style="height:18.6pt">
    <td width="78" colspan="2" valign="top" style="width:58.85pt;border:solid windowtext .5pt;
  padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:18.6pt">
      <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:-7.1pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
  inter-ideograph">&nbsp;<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
      </o:p>
      </span></p>
    </td>
    <td width="136" valign="top" style="width:101.65pt;border:solid windowtext .5pt;
  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;
  height:18.6pt">
      <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:-7.1pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
  inter-ideograph"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes; font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
      </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
  &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">来说</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
      </o:p>
      </span></p>
    </td>
    <td width="157" valign="top" style="width:117.7pt;border:solid windowtext .5pt;
  border-left:none;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;
  height:18.6pt">
      <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:-7.1pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
  inter-ideograph"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes; font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
      </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
  &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">说来</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
      </o:p>
      </span></p>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="height:15.95pt">
    <td width="36" rowspan="2" valign="top" style="width:26.75pt;border:solid windowtext .5pt;
  border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;
  height:15.95pt">
      <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:-7.1pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
  inter-ideograph"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes; font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp; 
      </span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
  &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">不同之处</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
      </o:p>
      </span></p>
    </td>
    <td width="43" valign="top" style="width:32.1pt;border-top:none;border-left:none;
  border-bottom:solid windowtext .5pt;border-right:solid windowtext .5pt;
  mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;
  padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:15.95pt">
      <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:-7.1pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
  inter-ideograph"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;
  font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
  &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">意义</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;
  mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
      </o:p>
      </span></p>
    </td>
    <td width="136" valign="top" style="width:101.65pt;border-top:none;border-left:
  none;border-bottom:solid windowtext .5pt;border-right:solid windowtext .5pt;
  mso-border-top-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;mso-border-left-alt:solid windowtext .5pt;
  padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:15.95pt">
      <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:-7.1pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
